() Tj
T*
(- The engine is not complete for full Pilgrim gameplay.) Tj
T*
(- The solver score is not final-game scoring quality.) Tj
T*
(- This is not strategic proof or balance validation.) Tj
T*
(- Only the current deterministic mancala-sandbox slice is covered.) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(Typical development workflow) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(1. Edit rules/config/scenario files.) Tj
T*
(2. Run `validate` to ensure scenario integrity.) Tj
T*
(3. Run `legal-actions` to inspect generated action space.) Tj
T*
(4. Run `solve` with a small depth to sanity-check transitions/search loop.) Tj
T*
(5. Run `pytest` to protect behavior with tests.) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(Troubleshooting) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(- `zsh: command not found: python`) Tj
T*
(  - Use `python3` instead of `python`.) Tj
T*
(  - Optional alias:) Tj
T*
(    `echo 'alias python=python3' >> ~/.zshrc && source ~/.zshrc`) Tj
T*
(- Scenario path errors) Tj
T*
(  - Confirm file exists: `scenarios/mancala_sandbox_001.json`.) Tj
T*
(  - Run commands from repository root.) Tj
T*
(- Validation fails) Tj
T*
(  - Check JSON syntax and current invariants \(acolyte conservation, non-negative ) Tj
T*
(resources, legal route lengths\).) Tj
T*
(- Solver output seems surprising) Tj
T*
(  - Inspect `legal-actions` first.) Tj
T*
(  - Remember the current scoring function is a temporary placeholder.) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(Next planned CLI improvements) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(- Clearer validation diagnostics \(which invariant failed and why\).) Tj
T*
(- Optional JSON output mode for tools/integration.) Tj
T*
(- Scenario diff helpers for fast debugging.) Tj
T*
(- Replay/event export commands for transition traces.) Tj
T*
(- Additional solver options beyond exact depth-limited search.) Tj
ET
